<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Franklin" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Franklin,</orth> a yeoman: <cit><quote>let boors and --s say it,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 5.2.173" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. V, 2, 173</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a f. in the wild of Kent,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.1.60" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 1, 60</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>no costlier than would fit a --'s housewife,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 3.2.79" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 2, 79</bibl></cit>.
